will automatically be added to the group for your school. Your profile information is needed by the STARS Evaluation team, so please keep it up to date. New students also need to complete a separate survey, the link is sent in the activation email.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Groups</strong></p>\r\n<p>Affinity groups are for anyone interested in certain topics. Please join the ones you are interested in. Through a group you can email group members, upload photos and videos, create events, and have discussions.</p>\r\n<p>Faculty members can create new groups. If you have a team of students, or want a new affinity group, talk to your local faculty member to create the group for you.</p>\r\n<p>Group admins can post announcements in groups. If you want to be an admin for a group, please message the current admins of that group.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n<p><strong>Files</strong></p>\r\n<p>You can share files attached to discussions. To upload a file, go to the discussion (or create a new one).</p>\r\n<p>To view files, you can view all files attached to a discussion, or go to View Group File to search and browse all files for a group.<strong>NOTE: You must allow pop-ups from this site for file downloading to work.</strong></p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p><strong>Events</strong></p>\r\n<p>You can create events for all of STARS, or within groups. You will receive on-site and emailed reminders to complete activity reports for your events. The link to the activity report is on the event view, as well as a link to indicate that you have completed the activity report.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</p>','2012-08-20 17:59:51','{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(21,66,45,1,'Test announcement','<p>Example of an announcement</p>','2012-11-05 17:16:57','{\"filepermission-member\":\"1\"}'),(33,99,823,1,'OCT 23 EA Meeting','<p>This will be our first Cohort EA Meeting. Setting it for Wednesday via Google Hangout</p>','2013-10-18 16:26:42','{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(32,64,45,1,'Do we get emails for announcements anymore','<p>Testing testing</p>','2013-10-03 14:26:26','{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(31,95,823,1,'Oct 03 Meeting 3:00 pm','<p>Due to several technical difficulties we are having our first EA Cohort Meeting this Wednesday. We will select the official date and time from here on out then.</p>','2013-09-30 19:08:31','{\"filepermission-member\":0}'),(30,3,77,1,'Outreach Images','<p>Hi UNCC STARS,</p>\r\n<p>As the semester is winding down, please upload any good outreach images you\'ve gathered this semester. We\'ll use them for a number of things... websites, flyers, newsletters, etc. We\'re always looking for new images of the exciting things you are all doing!</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Thanks,<br />Scott</p>','2013-04-25 15:06:23','{\"filepermission-member\":0}');
